snippet.title: Sluggish Morss (Blind Playthrough - No Commentary)
snippet.description:
So... I had this in my games folder for a while and never played it. Glad(?) I did. This game also reminds me of Hotline Miami in some ways...
I might play the sequel (Sluggish Morss: A Delicate Time in History) if people want me to. 
Download the game here: http://gamejolt.com/games/other/sluggish-morss/12218/
Download the sequel here: http://gamejolt.com/games/other/sluggish-morss-a-delicate-time-in-history/12298/
